373
00:31:34,258 --> 00:31:36,216
What did the police say?

374
00:31:36,216 --> 00:31:38,978
They haven't been informed of any missing children recently.

375
00:31:38,978 --> 00:31:41,842
They recorded it in their incident report.

376
00:31:41,842 --> 00:31:43,949
I think we must look after Jigsaw for a while.

377
00:31:43,949 --> 00:31:46,782
Wait until someone contacts us.

378
00:31:46,782 --> 00:31:49,540
Can the two of us handle him?

379
00:31:49,540 --> 00:31:52,620
