425
00:34:48,927 --> 00:34:52,042
Pakorn took such good care of my body.

426
00:34:52,042 --> 00:34:55,162
Wait. Look at this news.

427
00:34:56,282 --> 00:34:57,543
Sounds possible?

428
00:34:57,543 --> 00:35:00,157
"Puen on a luxurious dinner date with a famous leading actress."

429
00:35:00,157 --> 00:35:02,740
"Or are they a real couple off-screen?"

430
00:35:03,682 --> 00:35:06,310
That's the news from a long time ago.

431
00:35:06,310 --> 00:35:08,780
It was even before I traveled to that universe.

432
00:35:10,097 --> 00:35:12,437
You told me you had never been in a relationship, didn't you?

433
00:35:14,275 --> 00:35:15,674
I had never been in a relationship.

434
00:35:15,674 --> 00:35:20,868
