476
00:38:46,932 --> 00:38:49,480
Please. Give me one airplane.

477
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:52,576
Please.

478
00:38:53,890 --> 00:38:55,180
Here.

479
00:38:55,180 --> 00:38:58,385
