493
00:39:57,400 --> 00:39:59,219
Raising a kid is not easy at all.

494
00:39:59,219 --> 00:40:02,519
If we figure out a solution together, everything will get better.

495
00:40:02,519 --> 00:40:04,952
My plan of surprising you that day hasn't been completed yet.

496
00:40:04,952 --> 00:40:07,547
